<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/217329.Gotham"><img alt="Gotham: A History of New York City to 1898" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386924946l/217329._SX98_.jpg" />
</a>

  
<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
