<li class='cover' id='bookCover_25326049'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/25326049-new-amsterdam"><img alt="New Amsterdam: The History of the Dutch Settlement Before It Became New York City" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1430219971l/25326049._SX98_.jpg" />
